## gpio-ranges

**Value type:** `<prop-encoded-array>`

Specifies the mapping between a GPIO controller and a pin controller. This property enables pinctrl-gpio cooperation. The format is one or more entries of `<pinctrl-phandle gpio-base pin-base count>`, where:

- *pinctrl-phandle*: phandle to the pin controller node
- *gpio-base*: first GPIO number in this range
- *pin-base*: first pin number in the pin controller for this range
- *count*: number of pins in this range

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun50i-h6.dtsi */
pio: pinctrl@300b000 {
    gpio-controller;
    gpio-ranges = <&pio 0 0 256>;
};
```
